		<h1 style="text-align: center">Biography</h1>
		<hr>
	</div>

	<div>
		<p>
		Raymond Etornam Agbeame is a Ghanaian computer programmer. He studied Computer 
		Science at the Kwame Nkrumah University of Science and Technology in Kumasi Ghana.
		Professionally, he has worked in the San Francisco Bay Area for  <a href="https://www.mozilla.org">Mozilla 
		Corporation</a> and the now-defunct company <a href="https://rocketfuel.com">Rocketfuel Inc</a>. 
		He currently works for <a href="https://www.collectivehealth.com">CollectiveHealth Inc</a>.
		</p>
		<p>He  is <a href="https://www.twitter.com">@retornam</a> on Twitter.</p>
	</div>
